  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/wearables/\" rel=\"tag\">佩戴产品</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"cn.engadget.com/2014/02/16/marty-mcflys-power-laces-will-arrive-in-2015/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/adam/18c9bb2a415381c269edaf5dbf3853b5/ku-xlarge.gif\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n话说曾在《回到未来 2》电影中 ，主角 Marty McFly 所穿出现的那对 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2011/09/09/nike-unveils-the-2011-mag-shoe-to-auction-off-1500-pairs-of-the/\">Nike MAG</a> 曾在 2011 年为了慈善而推出，不过它让人有点失望就是没有电影中出现的电动鞋带功能（Power Laces）。幸好 Nike 设计师 Tinker Hatfield 已经确认了一款将在 2015 年推出的 MAG 会具备电动鞋带，不知道届时它会不会又是一款为慈善而推出的球鞋呢？如果是的话，那麽恐怕大家都负责不起了。最后顺带一提，2011 年推出的那款现在仍然在 eBay 上有售，只是开价 US$8,000（约人民币 48,530 元）「而已」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[图片来源：<a href=\"http://gizmodo.com/nike-designer-says-marty-mcflys-power-laces-are-coming-1523547123?utm_campaign=socialflow_gizmodo_twitter&amp;utm_source=gizmodo_twitter&amp;utm_medium=socialflow\">Gizmodo</a>]<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://gizmodo.com/nike-designer-says-marty-mcflys-power-laces-are-coming-1523547123?utm_campaign=socialflow_gizmodo_twitter&amp;utm_source=gizmodo_twitter&amp;utm_medium=socialflow\">Gizmodo</a><br />\n引用来源：<a href=\"http://solecollector.com/news/tinker-hatfield-confirms-nike-mag-will-release-with-power-laces-20151/\">Sole Collector</a><br />\n<br />\n </div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/16/marty-mcflys-power-laces-will-arrive-in-2015/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20831165/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/16/marty-mcflys-power-laces-will-arrive-in-2015/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
